parameters: Or, maybe check out other rooms

(And I had a impressed memory about her)
Don't tell me you're still hung over...
After I got off the phone with you, for some reason the stairs appeared again
跟你打完电话之后楼梯不知道为什么又重新出现
So I ran to you immediately, what do you think? is this enough concern for you?

Are you still think of something?
As a member of SOS Supernatrual Research Club, why aren't you excited about that?

Freelyn...have you ever seen me today?
菲林你……白天有见过我吗？
Tell me the story on you
跟我说下你那边发生的事情

I don't know why, but my memory is kind of messed up

不过还是一五一十地告诉了菲林

但在我的记忆里我才刚跟你打完电话
难道是我的记忆出了问题吗？
To be honest, I always feel strange since I've been this school
说实话，我一直都觉得这学校很奇怪
In here, something seems out of place
在这所学校里，我总会感觉到突兀以及违和

All along, I'm collecting other people's stories

How did you get back here once you left

How did I get out here...and why I came back...
我又是怎么出去的呢……又是怎么回来的呢……
It just like my memory has been deleted, I can't remember at all
